Package: TreeDetectR
Title: Detecting and segmenting individual urban trees from LiDAR point cloud 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Fyeqa", "Akram", , "fyeqaakram30@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to classify ground points, generate canopy height models, detect tree tops, and segment individual trees from urban LiDAR point cloud data.
